                     \underbrace{\begin{bmatrix} I \\
                      {𝐯^⊤ \over \sqrt{α}} & \sqrt{α}
                                        \end{bmatrix}}_{U_1^⊤}
$$
By assumption $K - {𝐯 𝐯^⊤ \over α} = ŨŨ^⊤$. 


**END**

